    <item>
      <title>To Do: A Checklist for Your Life</title>
      <link>http://luissantos.pt/post/2013-08-01-to-do-a-checklist-for-your-life/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2013 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://luissantos.pt/post/2013-08-01-to-do-a-checklist-for-your-life/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Now i&#39;m almost turning 26 i will follow an advice and create a &#34;To Do List&#34; for my life.&lt;br /&gt;
Some items i just Borrowed from other but i will keep adding my own.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;run a marathon&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Watch a movie at a drive-in&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set foot on every continent&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Live by myself&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Achieve your person&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Make a meal entirely from your own garden&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;del&gt;Travel by myself&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;del&gt;Date an Italian Woman&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Figure out a life hobby&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Find my career (or at least be close to finding it)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Learn how to speak another language&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Do yoga&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write a book&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skydive&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sleep in the desert&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take a swim in every ocean&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;.....&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Let the games begin....&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
